      "writtenOn": "2020-05-28T00:08:57Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It does.\nIterator cannot be reused so I can\u0027t move them to a separate @compute.\nI\u0027ll add a \u0027CachedIterator\u0027 in a separate CL to address that.",
